              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_dash_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Where does the name “UNNAP” come from?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_MmWtwF": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "t:names.text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>It’s a nod to breaking free from oversleeping — a reminder to stop “napping” on your mornings and start living them.</p>",
